{"type": "article", "id": 24297, "title": "带有建筑纹饰的方凳", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-23T07:00:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104502CdUG17ev4aJ3qiD0.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组方凳的纹路来自不同建筑的柱子，设计师 Nynke Koster 将历史上不同时期的建筑饰物翻模，然后用橡胶、木头、泡沫塑料等材料制作。可以看到古典、巴洛克、现代等多个风格，拥有强烈的装饰性和对比，在熟悉之中带有点后现代。将经典建筑风格融入到工业设计中是一个很聪明的办法。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104500YA0x7zmQq8X5EFnM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.25833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104500n16GlQgtpmEbPhoj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.27966102\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104501PKgyqEUuaDp1wRCZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55104167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104501ln4G6McWg25XBeyQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104501qWX3bR7UAzopgLr4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71354167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}